# Behavioral Preferences and Price Risk Management: A Systematic Literature Review

This repository contains the materials our systematic literature review study to to identify behavioral factors 
that influence the adoption of financial tools for price risk management in agriculture.  

## Project Structure

BehavPriceRiskManagement/
├── 1_data/
    ├── IncludedStudies_FinalList.ris  # RIS file of included studies
    └── Data_SLR_BehavPriceRisk.xlsx   # data 
├── 2_scripts/ 
    └── Script_SLR_BehavPriceRisk.R    # R scripts for data analysis 
├── 3_results/                         # Outputs: figures, tables
├── 4_manuscripts/                     # Final reports
└── README.md                          # This file

## How to Run 

1. Open the project by double-clicking.

2. Run script: "2_scripts/Script_SLR_BehavPriceRisk.R"